                        "description":  "Use a 250+ GP forked metal rod attuned to a plane of existence while the caster and up to eight willing creatures link hands in a circle. The destination can be a general place on another plane with near-arrival determined by the DM, or a known sigil sequence for a teleportation circle on another plane; if that circle is too small, transported creatures spill into the closest unoccupied spaces.",
